{"data":[{"id":2033,"slug":"the-max-level-hero-has-returned","title":"The Max Level Hero has Returned!","alt_titles":["最終レベル英雄のご帰還","Max Level Hero","The Max Level Hero Strikes Back!","The Max Leveled Hero Will Return!","O Herói de Nível Máximo Retornou","The Max Level Hero Strikes Back","만렙 영웅님께서 귀환하신다!","การกลับมาของวีรบุรุษเวลตัน","顶级英雄归来","Возвращение героя максимального уровня","英雄大人滿級回歸","Max Level Hero Is Making a Comeback!"],"description":"\u003cp\u003eThe weak prince of an insignificant country, Davey. After becoming comatose, his soul escaped to a temple where the souls of heroes gathered. He trained for a thousand years and has now returned as a max level hero!!“Just you guys wait, I’m gonna face you all head on!”The refreshing story of Davey’s royal life and revenge has just begun.\u003c/p\u003e","cover":"https://cdn.asurascans.com/asura-images/covers/the-max-level-hero-has-returned.9cc9f9.webp","banner":"https://cdn.asurascans.com/asura-images/banners/the-max-level-hero-has-returned.13e13c.webp","status":"ongoing","type":"manhwa","author":"Devil's tail","artist":"Yudo","popularity_rank":74,"bookmark_count":30337,"rating":8.155813953488373,"chapter_count":238,"last_chapter_at":"2026-06-29T20:43:22.152081Z","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-01T07:41:22.9388Z","public_url":"/comics/the-max-level-hero-has-returned-30e93729","source_url":"/s/2033","genres":[{"id":1,"name":"Action","slug":"action"},{"id":4,"name":"Adventure","slug":"adventure"},{"id":16,"name":"Fantasy","slug":"fantasy"},{"id":24,"name":"Isekai","slug":"isekai"}],"latest_chapters":[{"id":259676,"series_id":0,"number":238,"slug":"chapter-238","page_count":0,"is_premium":false,"comments_enabled":false,"early_access_until":"2026-06-30T02:43:22.152081Z","published_at":"2026-06-29T20:43:22.152081Z","view_count":0,"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},{"id":259519,"series_id":0,"number":237,"slug":"chapter-237","page_count":0,"is_premium":false,"comments_enabled":false,"early_access_until":"2026-06-23T10:32:28.247214Z","published_at":"2026-06-23T04:32:28.247214Z","view_count":0,"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},{"id":259243,"series_id":0,"number":236,"slug":"chapter-236","page_count":0,"is_premium":false,"comments_enabled":false,"early_access_until":"2026-06-09T03:01:59.286Z","published_at":"2026-06-08T21:01:59.286Z","view_count":0,"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"}]},{"id":2202,"slug":"world-saving-is-a-skill","title":"World-Saving is a Skill","alt_titles":["The One Who Saved a World Before Will Be Best at Saving Another","The Return of the World Savior","A Hero Who Knows His Stuff","세상도 구해본 놈이 잘 구한다"],"description":"\u003cp\u003eI saved another world... only to find Earth in an even bigger mess.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eHowever, there's no need to worry. A guy who saved the world once can do it again.\u003c/p\u003e","cover":"https://cdn.asurascans.com/asura-images/covers/world-saving-is-a-skill.6a3c10.webp","status":"ongoing","type":"manhwa","author":"Anakpil","artist":"Studio JHS","popularity_rank":116,"bookmark_count":10581,"rating":8.478527607361963,"chapter_count":33,"last_chapter_at":"2026-06-29T01:41:13.687947Z","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-01T07:41:16.834137Z","public_url":"/comics/world-saving-is-a-skill-30e93729","source_url":"/s/2202","genres":[{"id":1,"name":"Action","slug":"action"},{"id":4,"name":"Adventure","slug":"adventure"},{"id":7,"name":"Comedy","slug":"comedy"},{"id":16,"name":"Fantasy","slug":"fantasy"}],"latest_chapters":[{"id":259651,"series_id":0,"number":32,"slug":"chapter-32","page_count":0,"is_premium":false,"comments_enabled":false,"early_access_until":"2026-06-29T07:41:13.687947Z","published_at":"2026-06-29T01:41:13.687947Z","view_count":0,"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},{"id":259551,"series_id":0,"number":31,"slug":"chapter-31","page_count":0,"is_premium":false,"comments_enabled":false,"early_access_until":"2026-06-25T20:44:54.686414Z","published_at":"2026-06-25T14:44:54.686414Z","view_count":0,"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},{"id":259361,"series_id":0,"number":30,"slug":"chapter-30","page_count":0,"is_premium":false,"comments_enabled":false,"early_access_until":"2026-06-15T12:53:22.797107Z","published_at":"2026-06-15T06:53:22.797107Z","view_count":0,"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"}]},{"id":1924,"slug":"the-hero-returns","title":"The Hero Returns","alt_titles":["Yeongung, Hoegwihada","El héroe regresa","英雄归来","英雄、回帰する","英雄回帰する","重新覺醒的英雄","Hero Returns","Hero, Returns","عودة البطل","영웅, 회귀하다"],"description":"\u003cp\u003eThe strongest hero of humanity, Kim Sung Bin.He threw everything on the line and fought... but he still couldn't prevent the destruction of the world.However, his legend has just begun as he returns 20 years into the past.\"I'll definitely... kill it this time.\"Now fully equipped with overwhelming power and experience, the hero's raid isn't over yet!\u003c/p\u003e","cover":"https://cdn.asurascans.com/asura-images/covers/the-hero-returns.87c539.webp","banner":"https://cdn.asurascans.com/asura-images/banners/the-hero-returns.f67a85.webp","status":"ongoing","type":"manhwa","author":"Black Ajin","artist":"Ant Studio","popularity_rank":91,"bookmark_count":31519,"rating":7.542728635682159,"chapter_count":160,"last_chapter_at":"2026-06-28T11:50:50.075239Z","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-01T07:41:16.864131Z","public_url":"/comics/the-hero-returns-30e93729","source_url":"/s/1924","genres":[{"id":1,"name":"Action","slug":"action"},{"id":4,"name":"Adventure","slug":"adventure"},{"id":16,"name":"Fantasy","slug":"fantasy"},{"id":34,"name":"Murim","slug":"murim"},{"id":55,"name":"Shounen","slug":"shounen"}],"latest_chapters":[{"id":259626,"series_id":0,"number":160,"slug":"chapter-160","page_count":0,"is_premium":false,"comments_enabled":false,"early_access_until":"2026-06-28T17:50:50.075239Z","published_at":"2026-06-28T11:50:50.075239Z","view_count":0,"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},{"id":259493,"series_id":0,"number":159,"slug":"chapter-159","page_count":0,"is_premium":false,"comments_enabled":false,"early_access_until":"2026-06-21T17:45:53.540413Z","published_at":"2026-06-21T11:45:53.540413Z","view_count":0,"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},{"id":259333,"series_id":0,"number":158,"slug":"chapter-158","page_count":0,"is_premium":false,"comments_enabled":false,"early_access_until":"2026-06-14T01:59:39.888965Z","published_at":"2026-06-13T19:59:39.888965Z","view_count":0,"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"}]},{"id":2176,"slug":"the-cold-blooded-warrior","title":"The Cold-Blooded Warrior","alt_titles":["血も涙もない勇者、ハッピーエンドの彼方へ","无血无泪的勇者","沒血沒淚的勇士","The Merciless Hero","피도 눈물도 없는 용사"],"description":"\u003cp\u003eHan Jaewoo is a sweat in the world-famous game \"Savior Of Humanity.\"\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eOnce a hardcore player, now drowning in debt in his tiny room.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eHis long-awaited showdown with a demon lord ends in an unexpected failure.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe debt collectors are closing in... and all that's left to him are despair and stubborn grit.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThat's when Aquila, the administrator, appears with an offer:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\"Don't you want to see it? The true happy ending of this game...\"\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWith a prize of 25 million dollars on the line, and the path to the true ending finally revealed, he accepts it.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eHowever, there's a catch:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eHe's thrown back into the game world with all his stats reduced to rock bottom.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\"Thanks for the \"realism,\" Aquilla...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eScrew it. I'm clearing this damn thing!\"\u003c/p\u003e","cover":"https://cdn.asurascans.com/asura-images/covers/the-cold-blooded-warrior.334bcd.webp","banner":"https://cdn.asurascans.com/asura-images/banners/the-cold-blooded-warrior.jpg","status":"ongoing","type":"manhwa","author":"Jin","artist":"Redice Studio","popularity_rank":150,"bookmark_count":6894,"rating":7.647058823529412,"chapter_count":60,"last_chapter_at":"2026-06-26T05:05:24.705176Z","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-01T07:41:10.399576Z","public_url":"/comics/the-cold-blooded-warrior-30e93729","source_url":"/s/2176","genres":[{"id":1,"name":"Action","slug":"action"},{"id":4,"name":"Adventure","slug":"adventure"},{"id":16,"name":"Fantasy","slug":"fantasy"}],"latest_chapters":[{"id":259576,"series_id":0,"number":60,"slug":"chapter-60","page_count":0,"is_premium":false,"comments_enabled":false,"early_access_until":"2026-06-26T11:05:24.705176Z","published_at":"2026-06-26T05:05:24.705176Z","view_count":0,"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},{"id":259444,"series_id":0,"number":59,"slug":"chapter-59","page_count":0,"is_premium":false,"comments_enabled":false,"early_access_until":"2026-06-19T15:24:46.195956Z","published_at":"2026-06-19T09:24:46.195956Z","view_count":0,"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},{"id":259305,"series_id":0,"number":58,"slug":"chapter-58","page_count":0,"is_premium":false,"comments_enabled":false,"early_access_until":"2026-06-12T18:43:28.995894Z","published_at":"2026-06-12T12:43:28.995894Z","view_count":0,"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"}]},{"id":2194,"slug":"the-demon-king-overrun-by-heroes","title":"The Demon King Overrun by Heroes","alt_titles":["Too Many Heroes for One Demon King","마왕인데 용사가 너무 많음","Kiếp Này Ma Vương Ta Không Theo Chuẩn Mực Nữa","The Demon King Has Too Many Heroes","Ma Vương Hồi Quy Dẹp Bỏ Tiêu Chuẩn Rác Rưởi, Tự tạo dựng đế chế riêng","หยุดนะจอมมาร ฮีโร่ล้อมไว้หมดแล้ว"],"description":"After diligently following the “demon king’s standards,” I ended up getting killed by the heroes.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhat, my tower and I are a custom-made hunting ground for heroes now?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWith this chance at life regained through regression, to hell with the damn demon king’s standards!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis is the story of surviving as the hard-headed(?) demon king, Berje!\u003c/p\u003e","cover":"https://cdn.asurascans.com/asura-images/covers/the-demon-king-overrun-by-heroes.6abc35.webp","banner":"https://cdn.asurascans.com/asura-images/banners/the-demon-king-overrun-by-heroes.jpg","status":"ongoing","type":"manhwa","author":"Fine Particles","artist":"Midnight Studio","popularity_rank":67,"bookmark_count":32216,"rating":9.60394265232975,"chapter_count":36,"last_chapter_at":"2026-06-25T20:18:24.962293Z","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-01T07:41:10.329749Z","public_url":"/comics/the-demon-king-overrun-by-heroes-30e93729","source_url":"/s/2194","genres":[{"id":1,"name":"Action","slug":"action"},{"id":4,"name":"Adventure","slug":"adventure"},{"id":7,"name":"Comedy","slug":"comedy"},{"id":16,"name":"Fantasy","slug":"fantasy"},{"id":43,"name":"Regression","slug":"regression"},{"id":48,"name":"Revenge","slug":"revenge"}],"latest_chapters":[{"id":259564,"series_id":0,"number":36,"slug":"chapter-36","page_count":0,"is_premium":false,"comments_enabled":false,"early_access_until":"2026-06-26T02:18:24.962293Z","published_at":"2026-06-25T20:18:24.962293Z","view_count":0,"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},{"id":259434,"series_id":0,"number":35,"slug":"chapter-35","page_count":0,"is_premium":false,"comments_enabled":false,"early_access_until":"2026-06-19T07:04:51.676796Z","published_at":"2026-06-19T01:04:51.676796Z","view_count":0,"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},{"id":259297,"series_id":0,"number":34,"slug":"chapter-34","page_count":0,"is_premium":false,"comments_enabled":false,"early_access_until":"2026-06-12T04:06:40.629635Z","published_at":"2026-06-11T22:06:46.216657Z","view_count":0,"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"}]},{"id":2160,"slug":"the-hero-starts-over-at-the-academy","title":"The Hero Starts Over at the Academy","alt_titles":["元天才英雄、アカデミーでやり直す","Moto Tensai Eiyuu, Academy de Yarinaosu","천재 영웅은 아카데미에서 다시 시작한다","Новое начало героя в академии","英雄在学院重新开始"],"description":"\u003cp\u003eMisato Kyoichiro, the leader of the strongest group of adventurers, the \"Golden Seekers,\" was betrayed by his comrades and left to die.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\"I won't just die like this!!\"\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn his final moments, he activated a reincarnation spell. Kyoichiro successfully reincarnated twenty years later as a student named Asai Kyosuke, a wielder of the \"Void\" attribute.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\"Void\" is an attribute mocked for being \"attributeless,\" but Kyoichiro knew the truth of this attribute, thanks to the \"Time\" attribute he had in his previous life.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe \"Void\" attribute has the potential to surpass the \"Time\" attribute, which was seen as the strongest in his lifetime.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThus, reborn as Asai Kyosuke, he returns to the Adventurer Academy, determined to purge all evil from society; all to get revenge on his former comrades, who betrayed him out of greed.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAnd...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\"Asai Kyosuke, I won't let anyone look down on you ever again.\"\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e...to reach the peak of strength, something he could not achieve in his previous life.\u003c/p\u003e","cover":"https://cdn.asurascans.com/asura-images/covers/the-hero-starts-over-at-the-academy.ad022e.webp","status":"ongoing","type":"manga","author":"Amaike Nozomu","artist":"HykeComic","popularity_rank":149,"bookmark_count":8879,"rating":7,"chapter_count":60,"last_chapter_at":"2026-06-22T18:40:08.6358Z","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-01T07:41:10.359682Z","public_url":"/comics/the-hero-starts-over-at-the-academy-30e93729","source_url":"/s/2160","genres":[{"id":1,"name":"Action","slug":"action"},{"id":4,"name":"Adventure","slug":"adventure"},{"id":16,"name":"Fantasy","slug":"fantasy"},{"id":44,"name":"Reincarnation","slug":"reincarnation"},{"id":48,"name":"Revenge","slug":"revenge"}],"latest_chapters":[{"id":259517,"series_id":0,"number":60,"slug":"chapter-60","page_count":0,"is_premium":false,"comments_enabled":false,"early_access_until":"2026-06-23T00:40:08.6358Z","published_at":"2026-06-22T18:40:08.6358Z","view_count":0,"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},{"id":259371,"series_id":0,"number":59,"slug":"chapter-59","page_count":0,"is_premium":false,"comments_enabled":false,"early_access_until":"2026-06-16T00:30:38.793695Z","published_at":"2026-06-15T18:30:38.793695Z","view_count":0,"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},{"id":259241,"series_id":0,"number":58,"slug":"chapter-58","page_count":0,"is_premium":false,"comments_enabled":false,"early_access_until":"2026-06-09T01:26:53.782387Z","published_at":"2026-06-08T19:26:53.782387Z","view_count":0,"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"}]},{"id":1930,"slug":"return-of-the-disaster-class-hero","title":"Return of the Disaster-Class Hero","alt_titles":["재앙급 영웅님이 귀환하셨다","Возвращение героя уровня катастрофы","Resurrection of the Catastrophic Hero","A Disaster Class Hero Has Returned","การกลับมาของฮีโร่ระดับหายนะ","The Return of the Disaster-Class Hero Chapter","Felaket Kahramanın Dirilişi","The Return of the Disaster-Class Hero","بازگشت قهرمان سطح فاجعه","灾难级英雄归来","Return of the Disaster-Level Hero","災いクラスの俺様英雄の帰還","Jaeang-geup Yeongung-nim-i Gwihwan Hasyeotda","災難級英雄歸來"],"description":"\u003cp\u003eI was the greatest hero on Earth.\"But he's dead. How could the guy we've killed come back?\"\"I dunno. But if he can come back, just let him.\"I really came back after 20 years?\"Why're you so surprised? What? Did you do something to hurt your conscience?\"You bastards. Just you wait.   \u003c/p\u003e","cover":"https://cdn.asurascans.com/asura-images/covers/return-of-the-disaster-class-hero.e23831.webp","status":"ongoing","type":"manhwa","author":"HEATS","artist":"Redice Studio","popularity_rank":30,"bookmark_count":73573,"rating":9.383259911894273,"chapter_count":182,"last_chapter_at":"2026-06-17T21:05:42.859253